<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Type-Matching code completion</b></p><p>When an array type is expected, invoke the Type-Matching code completion (<span class="shortcut">&shortcut:SmartTypeCompletion;</span>) twice. The IDE will search for collections with the same component type and suggest converting them using the <span class="code_emphasis">toArray()</span> call.</p></body></html>